<parameter name="old_string">  {
    id: 'prompt-47',
    prompt: 'Create and practice a personalized grounding routine that combines physical movement, breathing exercises, and sensory awareness for managing anxiety or panic episodes',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Having a practiced, multi-sensory grounding routine provides immediate tools for managing acute anxiety, panic attacks, or overwhelming emotions when they arise. Combine techniques like progressive muscle relaxation, 4-7-8 breathing, and the 5-4-3-2-1 sensory method into a 5-10 minute sequence you can use anywhere. Practice this routine daily when calm so it becomes automatic during crisis moments, and consider recording yourself guiding through the steps to use when concentration is difficult.'
  }</parameter>
<parameter name="new_string">  {
    id: 'prompt-47',
    prompt: 'Create and practice a personalized grounding routine that combines physical movement, breathing exercises, and sensory awareness for managing anxiety or panic episodes',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Having a practiced, multi-sensory grounding routine provides immediate tools for managing acute anxiety, panic attacks, or overwhelming emotions when they arise. Combine techniques like progressive muscle relaxation, 4-7-8 breathing, and the 5-4-3-2-1 sensory method into a 5-10 minute sequence you can use anywhere. Practice this routine daily when calm so it becomes automatic during crisis moments, and consider recording yourself guiding through the steps to use when concentration is difficult.'
  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-48',
    prompt: 'Schedule a comprehensive mental health treatment review session with your primary provider to evaluate progress and plan the next phase of your care',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Regular comprehensive reviews ensure your treatment plan continues to evolve with your changing needs and progress, preventing stagnation and identifying new goals or approaches. Schedule a dedicated session focused solely on reviewing what\'s working, what challenges remain, and what adjustments might improve your outcomes. This proactive evaluation helps maintain momentum in your recovery journey and ensures you\'re getting maximum benefit from your time and investment in mental health treatment.'
  }</parameter>
</invoke>
